===Verb===
{{en-verb}}

# To draw a chart or map.
# To draw or figure out a route or plan.
#: "Let's '''chart''' how we're going to get from here to there."
# [intrans.] (of a record) appear on a hit-recording chart.
#: "The song has charted for 1500 weeks!"

